HEADWORD: Maksutov telescope
<hw>Maksutov telescope</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A type of reflecting
telescope in which the aberration of the concave mirror is reduced by a
meniscus lens.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

